      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, a masterclass in lightweight engineering and rotary performance. This example features the sequential twin-turbocharged 13B-REW power plant, maintaining exceptional compression across all rotor faces. The chassis retains its factory-spec 50/50 weight distribution and remains rigid, complemented by the original double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential for precise power delivery. Mechanically optimized with a full silicone vacuum line refresh and an upgraded aluminum radiator to ensure thermal management. The exterior retains its high-gloss factory finish, while the interior is free of the typical plastics degradation or bolster wear. A true collector-grade specimen with zero modifications to the intake or exhaust tracts, preserving the authentic FD driving dynamics.",
